{
  "chapter": 56,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十六回\"老而不死\"分三条线展开：万老夫人以美食诱惑胡不愁，胡不愁被迫屈服；海盗船上的独眼龙决定保护水天姬并喂她食物，水天姬恢复体力后展现威慑力，独眼龙请求她对付万老夫人；水天姬进入船舱与万老夫人对峙，以心理战术迫使万老夫人自点穴道并认输，万老夫人说出一个关于水天姬与方宝玉的秘密。与此同时，方宝玉潜入神秘湖泊，被水底裸女引入水宫之门，见到水宫少女，水宫少女以裸体出现并与宝玉展开关于穿衣与羞耻的对话。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "只要你说出来，不但这整个鸡腿是你的，还有这烧肉——猪肉；牛肉，还有洒着胡椒的羊肉，蒸得又白又大的馒头……",
      "tone": "诱惑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住口！……求求你，住口。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "你瞧，这猪肉烤得多好，肉皮又香又脆。还有这羊肉，肥肥的羊肉，你若夹在馒头里吃，只要轻轻咬一口，保险你一嘴都是油。",
      "tone": "诱惑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我说……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "text": "你肯说了么？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_bu_chou",
      "speaker_name": "胡不愁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我肯说了……我不是人……我肯说了……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "麻面汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想那老怪物这么大年纪了，还是个老风骚，竟还要弄个年轻的小伙子，关在舱里捣鬼。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_nao_dai",
      "speaker_name": "小脑袋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是这老风骚眼光也忒差了，选来选去，竟选了那么个大头猴子。那把瘦骨头，哪禁得起她折腾。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_dao_a",
      "speaker_name": "海盗甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这你就不懂了。就因为她年纪大了，所以才不敢找咱们，否则要散的可就是她那把老骨头。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_nao_dai",
      "speaker_name": "小脑袋",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你懂？你懂个屁！越老的才越有劲。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_dao_a",
      "speaker_name": "海盗甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既是如此，你为何不上？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鲳鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我小鲳鱼就算八年没见过女人，也不会要她，你瞧她那一身死肉……啐！",
      "tone": "嫌弃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鲳鱼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "何况这里还有个美人儿在等着，各位若是我的好兄弟，就让我小鲳鱼先拔个头筹如何？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "麻面汉子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那不行，她哪禁得起你？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_dao_b",
      "speaker_name": "海盗乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还是让我吧，我最斯文。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们都站在一边去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鲳鱼",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "龙老大若要，自然该龙老大占先的。",
      "tone": "谄媚",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "text": "不要。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鲳鱼",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "老大若是不要，那么我……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "text": "你到厨房弄碗热汤，弄块肉来。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鲳鱼",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "但……但咱们不能给她吃的。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "text": "谁说的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鲳鱼",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "那老……老……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "text": "你听她的，还是听我的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鲳鱼",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "但……但这女子若是有了气力，咱们只怕就动不了她了。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "text": "咱们本就不动她。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鲳鱼",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "但……但龙老大，这已是到嘴的肥肉，咱们为何大……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "text": "你想动她？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_chang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小鲳鱼",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "老大你也该可怜可怜小兄弟们，兄弟们已有七八个月没有上岸了，七八个月没见过女人，这滋味可真不是人受的。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有谁要说话？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们面上虽然听话，心里必定不服：龙老大与这女子非亲非故，为什么要强出头来放她？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_dao_group",
      "speaker_name": "海盗们",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "不……不是。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是不是？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_dao_group",
      "speaker_name": "海盗们",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但你们若认为龙老大不讲理，你们就错了。我要放这女子，自然是有缘故、有道理的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我且问你们，那老妖婆可恨不可恨？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_dao_group",
      "speaker_name": "海盗们",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可恨！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们若将这老妖婆带回岸上，还有没有脸去见头儿？就算头儿不怪咱们，但这种丢人的事若是传出去，咱们这条船还能在海上混么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_dao_group",
      "speaker_name": "海盗们",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这老怪物，老不死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们除了在嘴里骂，还能将她怎样？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_dao_group",
      "speaker_name": "海盗们",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们非但打也打不过她，就连骂也骂不过她。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就是了，咱们既然没法子，就得找人帮忙。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_dao_group",
      "speaker_name": "海盗们",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "找谁？在大海上咱们能找谁？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是这位姑娘。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_dao_group",
      "speaker_name": "海盗们",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她？……找她？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们这群呆鸟，难道未曾见到那老妖婆对这位姑娘是何等惧怕？若不是这位姑娘已饿得没有力气，那老妖婆只怕立刻就要跪下。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_dao_group",
      "speaker_name": "海盗们",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错……的确如此……到底是龙老大有头脑。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既已知道不错，还不快些将热汤送上。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谢谢你们。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我本来已准备死的，但你们却救了我，也救了他，我……我实在不知道该如何感激你们才好。",
      "tone": "感动",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "姑娘，你……在下……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "你放心，你们的事，包在我身上。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "那……那老妖婆……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "她这次再也逃不了的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "但……但像姑娘这样的人，也能下手杀人么？姑娘你可杀过人么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "我一个人也没有杀过。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "这……只……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "我没有杀过一个人……我只杀过五千多个。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "姑……姑娘还不去？",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "体力还未恢复就去，万一打起来怎么办？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "和姑娘一起上船的那位是……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "他叫胡不愁，他……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "你看他怎样？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "很好很好，只是……恐怕……稍微太弱了些。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "他弱？……嘿！他若不是被饿了十几天，像你们这样的人，他一个最少可以打你们八百五十个。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "是……是，但现在，他却是危险已极。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "危险？……他若真有危险，我还会躺在这里？他若真有危险，莫说我还能走，就是爬也要爬去的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "但……但那老妖婆。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "你放心，那老妖婆不会杀他的，就算他打了那妖婆八个耳光，就算他咬下那妖婆一只耳朵，那老妖婆也不敢动他的。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "因为那老妖婆有件事要求他。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "那老妖婆反而要求他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "嗯！你不相信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "但姑娘未曾瞧见，怎会知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "我不用瞧见也能猜得到的，他……",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老妖婆……这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "扶我进去。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "扶我过去。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "是，但……但……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "还但什么，快！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "但姑娘连走路的力气都没有，怎能……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_du_yan_long",
      "text": "谁说我连走路的气力都没有？我只不过要将每分力气都留给那妖婆，知道么？……快！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_yan_long",
      "speaker_name": "独眼龙",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "撞开门。",
      "tone": "命令",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "万老夫人，你好么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "你……你怎会……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "奇怪吧？其实我自己又何尝不奇怪。但我如今却已知道，饥饿虽是种可怕的病，但好得却很快。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "万老夫人，你怕什么呀？我最多也不过只能杀死你而已，最多也不过只能将你切成一块块的，抛进海里喂鲨鱼，这又有什么好怕的？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "水……水姑娘，我……我又没有对……对不起你们，你……你瞧，连我的耳朵都已被胡少侠咬掉了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "唷！这是怎么回事呀……哦！我猜着了，大概是胡不愁说话的声音太小，你听不清，所以将耳朵凑上去，哪知胡不愁却当真饿了，连你的耳朵都要吃，唉……他的胃口可真不错。",
      "tone": "格格笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "水姑娘猜得真不错，简直好像亲眼瞧见似的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "过奖过奖……但胡不愁说的究竟是什么好听的事呀？竟能使万老夫人也这么着急地想去听。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "他……他……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "哦，我知道了，他说的必定是紫衣侯武功之秘，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "什么事都瞒不过你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你既已听到紫衣侯武功之秘，现在武功想必进步很多了，只怕……只怕我已不再是你的敌手。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "那……哪有这么快？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "幸好没有这么快，否则我还想活么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "是……不是……是……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "我既然想活，你就莫要想活了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "水姑娘……求求你。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你若不等我动手，还可死得舒服些，否则……我！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "求求你，看在我儿子的分上，饶了我吧！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你儿子，你儿子是谁？关我屁事。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "水姑娘，只要你饶了我，我就说出件秘密，极大的秘密。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "你且先将“肩井”、“气血”、左右双膝关节的穴道点了，也许我还会听你说话。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "是，是。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "奇怪，你怎么真的不敢和我动手？其实我体力还没有完全恢复呀，你和我动手，我还真打不过你。",
      "tone": "娇笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "常听江湖人言，万老夫人宁可跪下求饶，也决不肯打没把握的架，所以才能活到现在，但这次你却上当了。",
      "tone": "格格笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "我输了……我输了，水姑娘当真厉害，我老婆子输得口服心服，比当真动过手还要服输。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "speaker_name": "水天姬",
      "listener": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "text": "好，那是什么秘密？你说吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_lao_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "万老夫人",
      "listener": "char_shui_tian_ji",
      "text": "好，我说，那秘密乃是有关水姑娘与方宝玉的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "水宫少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "方少侠才来么？我家娘娘已久等了。",
      "tone": "娇媚",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "水宫少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我身子很难看么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "text": "哪里……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "水宫少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我身子既不难看，方少侠为何不敢看我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "text": "这……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "水宫少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "方少侠可是因为我没穿衣裳？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "水宫少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "但方少侠可知人为什么要穿衣裳？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "text": "这……因为……人本是要穿衣裳的。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "水宫少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "但原因是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "text": "因为……因为御寒。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "水宫少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "但这里并不冷呀！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "text": "那么……便是因为羞耻之心。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "水宫少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "为何要有羞耻之心？父母生下的清白身子，为何不能给别人看……这只因人们本身有了罪恶之心，才会觉得羞耻，是么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "text": "咳……咳咳！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "水宫少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "所以衣裳本是罪恶之产物，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "text": "咳咳，还是相烦姑娘带在下去见宫主。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "水宫少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我先问你，我说的话对不对？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "text": "听来似乎不错。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "水宫少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "既然不错，就请方少侠也将衣服脱了吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shui_gong_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "水宫少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "方少侠身上莫非有些见不得人的地方？否则为何如此害怕？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们再过来，我就原路退回了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 56,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    }
